        <p>If there is anything on this platform that speaks to your heart, check in with your inner world and reach out with a full YES. If you are hesitant, have questions or need a bit more of an explanation, I will be at the other end making sure to get back at you</p>
        <p>Lobi,</p>
        <p>Nicole</p>

